skin-d3c029086736_1_st.description:
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

This item tracks Confirmed Kills.

Firing two large-mag Berettas at once will lower accuracy and increase load times. On the bright side, you'll get to fire two large-mag Berettas at once. This memento from Agency has a dark patina and grips of black limba wood.\n\nWhere classic construction meets modern aesthetics
